== Ganvachea Nanvacho Ithias ==

[[File:Regional Plan of Avedem along with the other neighbouring villages.jpg|thumb|Avedem ani tachea lagshirlea ganvcho regional plan]]
Oxi somjikai asa ki jedna Portuguese foujeche xipai Goem-che veg-vegle zage aplea tabeant ghetale tedna Dhorm porgottnar Portuguese xipaya borobor hea zagear pavle zaka atam Paroda mhunntat. Jedna te hea zagear pavle tedna tannkam thoim vhanvti nodi disli ani tannem mhullem “AQUI SEZA PARADE” mhunnje “Ami hanga thambu-ya” ani tea khatir tea zageak  “Parada” mhunnunk survat zali, kaim vorsam uprant hea zageachem nanvant durusti korun tem “Paroda” kelem. The Foujecho senapati hea zagear ravlo ani uprant ti nodi balandun vo hupun dusrea vatten pavlo ani tea zageak “Avde” mhunnon nanv dilem. Tea ugdassak tannem thoim ek Copel bandlem ani tem  “Livrament Saibinni-k” bhettoilem.
Tea uprant xezarchea “Avde”ganvant “Dessai” aile ani tea ganvant tannim “Cotombi” ani “Assolda” oxe vegle ganv toyear kele. Je Dssai Cotombi ganvant ailole te “Prabhu Dessai”-chea fuddarponna khala asle tor je Dessai Asolda ailole te “Raut Dessai”-chea fuddarponna khala asle.
Hea vattarantle Dessai uprant “Avde” yevun aplem pennem korunk lagle. Te hea ganvant yevchea adim thoim “Ganvkar” and “Gavdi” thoim apli vosti korun asle.  He ganvkar fokot xetant kam kortale zankam “Xetkar” mhunnon olkhotale. Te xetam roitale khore pun tim xetam tanchea malkechim naslim torui tanncheach modem jim xetam te roitat tim xetam aplinch mhunnon te mandtale. Hea somjikayen  tanncheach modem tannim aplim xetam vantlolim. Avde ailolea Dessai-ank thoddem xikxonn aslem tea khatir tannim ganvchea lokak te xetam roitat ti zomin tannchea nanvar korun ghevpachim kagot-potram ghevpak zai mhunnon xittkaile. Tannchem sangnnem aikun soglea xetkarani fatti fuddem kainch chinti nastna aplea xetachim kagot-potram aplea nanvar korunk Dessai-anchea tabeant kelim ani hem soglem korunk tankam aplo purai odhikar dilo. Xetkaranchea oxikxitponnacho faido ghevun Dessai-ani xetachi nondni kortana fokot panchvo vantto tannchea nanvar kelo ani baki zomin apli keli. Xetkari oxikxit aslolean tankam to unnav somzolona ani jem kitem tannkam dillem tem tannim manun ghetlem. Dessai ghoranneantlo sogleantlo zanto ani xrest monxean tea ganvachem nanv bodlun “Avedem” dovorlem.

