===Devull=== 

- Shree Saunsthan Shantadurga - Chamundeshwari Kudtari Mahamaya

Shree Saunsthan Shantadurga Chamundeshwari Kudatari Mahamaya, hem duvull Avedem hangchea guddo vaddeant sthaplolem asa. Poilim hem devull 1560 vorsa kristanvachea xekddeant Curtorim ganvche Sandiwal vo Sandel hea vaddeant aslolem. Punn 16 vea xekddeant, dhormik bodolnneche bhirantik lagun hangche Devbhokt ani her lokamni hangache devinchem sthan bodlun poilim Chandravadi xarantlea xelvonnea ganvant vheleo ani uprant teo Avedem ganvant ghuddo, hea vaddeant vhorun tanchi stapnni keli. Tem devull aiz pasun  Shree Saunsthan Shantadurga Chamundeshwari Kudatari Mahamaya hea nanvam guddo vaddeant asa. Ho ganv kepemchea talukent asa.

Mukel devi

Hea mondiracheo mukhel devi mhollear Shree Shantadurga and Shree Chamundeshwari Kudtari Mahamaya. Hea mondirache prottom murteo Shree Shantadurga and Shree Chamundeshwari Kudtari Mahamaya eka-mekache samkara Girbhagraha hatunt asat. Shree Chamundeshwari Shree Shantadurgechea uzvea vatten dovorleli asa.



Shree Udangi hi murti Shantadurga Chamundeshwati  Devull sthapn zaunche adim hea gavant axil’li. Hi murti hea Devllache samkar eka gruha(temple) hatunt asa. Shree Udangi, hi murti muechea- dongrahea akarant asa. 

Shree Laxminarayan, Shree Ganapati, Shree Mahadev, Shree Grampurush hanchi murti Shantadurga Chamundeshwari devllachea uzvea vattent stapit kelo

Tech porim, Shree Ravalnath hachi murti tea Devllache uzve vatten sthaploli asa. Hindu lok oxem mhantat kid or eka devllant tancho khaxa Ravalnnat asa zo lokanchi rakhonn korta.


Shree Jalmis hachi murti mukhel mondirache bhair eka daktulea fatrant asa. Tech borobar char Shree Mahrangan Shilas Udangi devlla mukhar ast.

===Zatra=== 

( Poush Pournima Zatrotsav)

[[File:Shree Saunsthan Shantadurga - Chamundeshwari Kudtari Mahamaya.jpg|thumb|Shree Saunsthan Shantadurga - Chamundeshwari Kudtari Mahamaya]]

Hea devllachem vorsa vollinchem fest mhollear Zatra (vo Poush Pournima Zatrotsav) hi Poush Punav hea disa zata. Hem fest tin dis mhonllear Paush : Shudha Trayodashi hea disamni zata. Hangche lok hem donui devi stapit korpacho dis pallunk hi zatra somorombdtat. 

Tryodashi, chatrodashi, punav hea tin disamni hi Zatra hangche lok somorombtat. Hea disamni sokallche hangche bhott obhishek kortat. Tem mhonlllear hea devllache donui murteank dudh, ghee, monv, god, ani sakor lavun nhannoitta. Hem choltonam te bhott  matrancho zap kortat. Oxem mhonntat montrancho zap kortanam teo devi tea murtint aplo akar getat ani teo murti povitr zatat. Uprant tea murtincher gondross(perfume) martat ani Chandan (sandlewood), kumkum and haldi pitto tea murtinchea kopllek laitat. Hem sogllem tanche dhormik vidi pormonnem te kortat. Uprant tea Devink te nhesoitat ani tanchi aarti kortat. Uprant hea Devink 
Neved (food for God) hem ditat. Sokallim neved mhollear follam.
 
Denparam, deivink bhangarachea nhesnnan nhesoitat ani tankam Neved ditat. Hea vellar neved mhonllelar xit, ani dureo khavpacheo vostu. Teo vostu uprant zoma zal’lea lokank te ditat. 



Sanjche vellar, te deivicheo dureo murti zatunt Devi aplo akar getat to vaprun palki toiar kortat. Tanheo dhomik vidhi palleo uprant teo Devi hea murtint aplo akar ghetat mhonn te mandtat. Ti Palki uprant devllache samkar bhonvddi korunk vortat. Uprant tea Devink panchgatt (food consisting of fruits) dakhoitat. Hem zoma zal’lea lokank te ditat. 
Hache uprant tea murti vorun mache  samkar dovortat. Macher Kalotsav mhonnge sankasur he danavak marpacho dekavo zata. Tea danavak marle uprant devink nitoll korpak lagxil’lea nhoint vortat. Thimsor tea Devincher udok xitkaitat, ani teo vhorun devllant dovortat.  Uprant zoma zal’lea lokank nattok polleunk mellta.
Dusrea ani tisrea disa osloch kareakrom zata. Dusrea disa sanjechi mayurasan(mhonnge morachi palki) hachi bhonvddi kortat. Hea disamni ratcho kalotsov korinant. To fokt poileach disa zata. 
Tin disa uprant chovtea disachea fatodder, te maharat- he voddli palki mondirachi bovddi korunk vortat. Hea rothacho bharr(weight)dha ton (10 tonn) asa oxem tanche ek bhott sangta.
Sokallche lok ekttaim zaun sangata zata te bhaxen ho Rath voddpak proitn kortat. Hea ratachi akhea devllachi bhonvddi kortat. Uprant to haddun suru zal’lea zagear haddun dovortat. Oxi hi zatra sompta.

